    "body": "Colony's build is [failing](https://circleci.com/gh/JoinColony/colonyNetwork/5323?utm_campaign=vcs-integration-link&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=github-checks-link), seems to be a result of the change in the above PR.\r\n\r\nRelevant CI output:\r\n```\r\n...\r\nSummary\r\n=======\r\n> Total deployments:   13\r\n> Final cost:          0 ETH\r\n\r\nError: [object Object]\r\n    at detectNetworkId (/home/circleci/colonyNetwork/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/truffle-core/lib/environment.js:73:1)\r\n    at <anonymous>\r\n    at process._tickCallback (internal/process/next_tick.js:182:7)\r\nTruffle v5.0.0-next.20 (core: 5.0.0-beta.2)\r\n```\r\n\r\nLooks like the error is constructed wrong [here](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/next/packages/truffle-core/lib/environment.js#L65-L74), although I might just be blanking on whether `{ message: \"...\" }` is kosher.\r\n\r\nHard to say if there's a real problem, we may have caught a mismatch in the test suite :)\r\n\r\nattn @eggplantzzz \r\ncc @elenadimitrova",
